quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  92,15,"Naatataange si wona ɓurɗo hiite."
  92,16,"OOn jedduɗo ɗuurnii."
  92,17,"Ma woɗɗita ngol ɓurɗo reentaade oon woni Abu Bakri yo weluyo Alla won e makko."
  92,18,"OOn tottiroowo jawdi mum ngam o laaɓa."
  92,19,"Alana hay go'oto ka makko neemo joɓeteeɗo."
  92,20,"Tawi wona ɗaɓɓude Alla ɓurɗo toowde O."
  92,21,"Mi wooɗndirii ma o wele."
  93,1,"Mi wooɗndirii e mbeeta."
  93,2,"Mi wooɗndarii jehma si mbo deeƴi."
  93,3,"Joom ma accaani mo o añaani."
  93,4,"Pellet ko galle La'akara ɓuri aduna o."
  93,5,"Arma joom ma okkuma ha mbeleɗa."
  93,6,"Mbele o tawaani ma ko a alyatiime o mool ma."
  93,7,"O tawma ko majjuɗo o feewnu ma."
  93,8,"O taw ma ko a ba'asɗo o alɗin ma."
  93,9,"Si tawi ko alyatiime woto hoynu ɗum."
  93,10,"Woto giddu ñaagatooɗo."
  93,11,"Si tawi ko ne'ema joom ma haal."
  94,1,"Mbele min n njaacnaani ma ɓernde ma."
  94,2,"Min ngittan ma bakkatuuji ma."
  94,3,"OOn nisnuɗo ke'eci ma."
  94,4,"Min ɓamtan ma innde ma."
  94,5,"Pellet kala saɗteende na won'di e newaare."
  94,6,"Pellet saɗteende kala na won'di e yaajeende."
  94,7,"Si a hantinii e (dewe alla)tampu."
  94,8,"E fa'ade joom ma reerɗu."